rows.label: tev055401_MSG0001
rows.name:
Zazazan was just talking to Bodada about
how to turn profit on this stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0002
rows.name:
And Zazazan had fantastic idea! We can use it to
make new type of food![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0003
rows.name:
Gooey-chewy dough ought to make really nice
dumplings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0004
rows.name:
Tasty new food will be called "Pickerupper Pollen
Pot Sticker"! ...Zazazan some kind of naming genius.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0005
rows.name:
Whole city will be talking about them! They probably
sell like hotcakes, except they are POT STICKERS![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0008
rows.name:
Meh heh heh! Loma will never suspect human chumps
snuck this into city for Zazazan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0009
rows.name:
Foolish Loma! Zazazan finally managed to outfox
stupid lapdog of elder![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0010
rows.name: Now Zazazan just have to... Meh? Friend AGAIN?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0011
rows.name:
Uh...friend should pretend not to hear any of that.
Zazazan very grateful for help with shipment,
so friend not hear ANYTHING.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0016
rows.name:
Meh-meh! Ganglion think they can invade city and
steal shipment of Zazazan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0017
rows.name:
Oh, everyone want Zazazan to take shelter on Ma-non
ship, but Zazazan say no way![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0018
rows.name:
Zazazan not want to be burden on Ma-non, so instead
Zazazan stay behind and brave fires of war to protect
this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055401_MSG0019
rows.name:
Besides, Zazazan get sentenced to permanent hard
labor if Ma-non find smuggled illega...
Uh, nothing! Never mind! Meh![ST:wait ]
